{"ID":"20220725153203-mcea6z0","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220725153203-mcea6z0","title":"Git","type":"doc","updated":"20220804223805"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220726200150-nj25mr8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220726200150-nj25mr8","updated":"20220726200152"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"问题"}]},{"ID":"20220726200153-nd6etc1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220726200153-nd6etc1","updated":"20220726200224"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"遇到出现Push to origin/master was rejected"}]},{"ID":"20220726200153-khtjw3c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220726200153-khtjw3c","updated":"20220726200212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220726200212-10dqref.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220726200228-vpx0q8f","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220726200228-vpx0q8f","updated":"20220726202517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cG93ZXJzaGVsbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#在 git 执行命令git push origin master时，报错error: failed to push some refs to ‘https://gitee.com/\n\n#根本原因是远程仓库和本地仓库内容不同，将远程仓库中不同的内容pull到本地，就好了。\n\n#比如，我是新建了一个远程仓库，准备把本地内容上传时，忘记把远程仓库的redme.md文件同步出错的。\n\ngit pull --rebase origin master\n\n#再次执行就好了\ngit push origin master\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220726200154-dtchxfy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220726200154-dtchxfy"}},{"ID":"20220725153203-amy3o7j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220725153203-amy3o7j","updated":"20220726200146"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Git作用"}]},{"ID":"20220725153240-0ou94jv","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220725153240-0ou94jv","updated":"20220725153304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220725153249-jktc54n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153249-jktc54n","updated":"20220725153249"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.代码回溯"}]},{"ID":"20220725153252-qk9xf1p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153252-qk9xf1p","updated":"20220725153256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.版本切换"}]},{"ID":"20220725153256-fc59zug","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153256-fc59zug","updated":"20220725153300"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.多人协作"}]},{"ID":"20220725153300-y18xluw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153300-y18xluw","updated":"20220725153304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.远程备份"}]}]},{"ID":"20220725153245-0bngqqo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220725153245-0bngqqo","updated":"20220725153331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Git概述"}]},{"ID":"20220725153334-kf7y0ug","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220725153334-kf7y0ug","updated":"20220725154545"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220725153333-15y49dl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153333-15y49dl","updated":"20220725154020"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Git是一个分布式版本控制工具，通常用来对软件开发过程中的源代码文件进行管理。通过Git仓库来存储和管理这些文件，Git仓库分为两种:"}]},{"ID":"20220725153959-34fuldp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153959-34fuldp","updated":"20220725154009"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地仓库:"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 开发人员自己电脑上的Git仓库"}]},{"ID":"20220725154001-76osagj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154001-76osagj","updated":"20220725154010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"远程仓库:"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 远程服务器上的Git仓库"}]},{"ID":"20220725154115-ipmcqnw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154115-ipmcqnw","updated":"20220725154116"}},{"ID":"20220725154116-r5xil1g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154116-r5xil1g","updated":"20220725154147"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"commit："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提交，将本地文件和版本信息保存到本地仓库"}]},{"ID":"20220725154200-17u2qhz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154200-17u2qhz","updated":"20220725154241"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"push："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"推送，将本地仓库文件和版本信息上传到远程仓库"}]},{"ID":"20220725154220-l3e5ns4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154220-l3e5ns4","updated":"20220725154243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"pull："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"拉取，将远程仓库文件和版本信息下载到本地仓库"}]},{"ID":"20220725154526-h6liktv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154526-h6liktv","updated":"20220725154528"}},{"ID":"20220725154528-s5o78ic","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725154528-s5o78ic","updated":"20220725154545"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"下载地址："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"https://git-scm.com/download/"}]}]},{"ID":"20220725153413-atz2d0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220725153413-atz2d0n","updated":"20220725154401"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"display: block; width: 33%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220725154351-hqr8m4o.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"display: block; width: 33%;\"}"}]},{"ID":